{"entries": {"Printer & Peripherals::my monitor screen is blank": {"question": "my monitor screen is blank", "normalized": "my monitor screen is blank", "response": "I'm happy to help you troubleshoot your issue with your monitor screen being blank. Let's get started!\n\n**Step 1: Check Physical Monitor**\n\n- Is the monitor properly plugged in and turned on? \n- Are there any signs of physical damage or wear on the monitor itself?\n\nPlease let me know if this helps, or if we need to move forward with other troubleshooting steps!\n\n📌 *I haven't forgotten — you also mentioned a **Hardware** issue. Once we resolve this one, just say 'next issue' and we'll tackle that.*", "category": "Printer & Peripherals", "kb_sources": [{"filename": "KB004_Printer_Issues.md", "category": "Printer & Peripherals", "preview": "## Troubleshooting Steps\n\n### Step 1: Check Physical Printer\n- Is the printer powered on? Check display panel\n- Check fo"}, {"filename": "KB004_Printer_Issues.md", "category": "Printer & Peripherals", "preview": "## When to Escalate\n- Hardware malfunction (error codes on display)\n- Printer needs physical repair/maintenance\n- Networ"}, {"filename": "KB004_Printer_Issues.md", "category": "Printer & Peripherals", "preview": "# KB004 — Printer & Printing Issues\n**Category:** Printer & Peripherals | **Priority:** P4 — Low | **Updated:** 2025-02-"}], "hit_count": 1, "created_at": "2026-04-07T14:27:04.294540", "last_hit": "2026-04-07T14:27:04.294540"}, "Network & VPN::in my laptop the network speed is slow the browser is taking 2 3 minutes to load the website": {"question": "in my laptop the network speed is slow the browser is taking 2-3 minutes to load the website", "normalized": "in my laptop the network speed is slow the browser is taking 2 3 minutes to load the website", "response": "**Step 1: Check Internet Connection**\n- Open a browser and visit https://www.google.com\n- If no internet, fix local WiFi/Ethernet first\n- If on WiFi, try switching to a wi